          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> 
            <a href="mailto:hello@thegroovelibrary.net">hello@thegroovelibrary.net</a>
          </p>
          <p>For general questions about The Groove Library, music submissions, or collaborations.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">Privacy & Data Requests</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> 
            <a href="mailto:privacy@thegroovelibrary.net">privacy@thegroovelibrary.net</a>
          </p>
          <p>For privacy-related questions, GDPR data requests, or cookie consent inquiries.</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Please include "GDPR Request" in the subject line for faster processing.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">Social Media</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Instagram:</strong> 
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/the_groove_library/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              @the_groove_library
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>Follow us for the latest mixes and updates.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="stack stack--md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl">Response Time</h2>
        <p>We strive to respond to all inquiries within:</p>
        <ul class="list list--bulleted">
          <li><strong>General inquiries:</strong> 3-5 business days</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy/GDPR requests:</strong> 1 month (as required by law)</li>
          <li><strong>Music submissions:</strong> 1-2 weeks</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
    
    <div class="stack stack--lg">
      <section class="stack stack--md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">How do I submit music?</h3>
          <p>Visit our <a href="/contribute/">Contribute page</a> for guidelines on submitting mixes and music for consideration.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">How do I exercise my GDPR rights?</h3>
          <p>Email <a href="mailto:privacy@thegroovelibrary.net">privacy@thegroovelibrary.net</a> with:</p>
          <ul class="list list--bulleted">
            <li>Your name and contact information</li>
            <li>Specific right you wish to exercise</li>
            <li>Any relevant details to help us locate your data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">How do I manage cookies?</h3>
          <p>You can manage cookie preferences at any time:</p>
          <ol class="list list--numbered">
            <li>Clear your browser cookies (resets all preferences)</li>
            <li>Use browser settings to block specific cookies</li>
            <li>Contact us to manually reset your cookie consent</li>
          </ol>
          <p>See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for more details.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stack stack--sm">
          <h3 class="text-xl">Can I use your mixes in my project?</h3>
          <p>All mixes are shared with permission from the artists. For usage requests, please contact us with details about your project.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="stack stack--md card card--outline">
        <h2 class="text-2xl">Quick Contact Tips</h2>
        <ul class="list list--bulleted">
          <li>Include relevant details in your first email</li>
          <li>For GDPR requests, use "GDPR Request" in subject line</li>
          <li>Check our FAQ before contacting</li>
          <li>Be patient - we're a small team passionate about music</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="stack stack--md text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl">Need Immediate Help?</h2>
    <p>For urgent matters, please include "URGENT" in your email subject line.</p>
